<section id="{{ filename }}" class="section">
    <div class="py-4 px-2 px-sm-4">
        <div class="section-heading mb-4">
            <a class="d-flex justify-content-between section-toggle text-decoration-none"
                data-bs-toggle="collapse" href="#{{ filename }}Collapse" role="button" 
                aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="{{ filename }}Collapse">
                <h2 class="display-6 w-100 d-flex m-0">
                    Reverse hex
                </h2>
                <span class="text-light px-1 border rounded align-self-end toggle-button">
                    <i class="bi bi-arrow-up lh-base"></i>
                </span>
            </a>
            <hr>
            <p class="px-2">
                Unlike reversing the entire string where <code class="d-inline-flex px-2 bg-success bg-opacity-10 border border-success border-opacity-10 rounded-2">48 65 6c 6c 6f</code> [Hello] becomes <code class="d-inline-flex px-2 bg-success bg-opacity-10 border border-success border-opacity-10 rounded-2">f6 c6 c6 56 84</code>, this reverses each individual hex byte in the same order. <code class="d-inline-flex px-2 bg-success bg-opacity-10 border border-success border-opacity-10 rounded-2">48 65 6c 6c 6f</code> becomes <code class="d-inline-flex px-2 bg-success bg-opacity-10 border border-success border-opacity-10 rounded-2">84 56 c6 c6 f6</code>. The Reverse Nibbles toggle reverses the order of each hex byte in the string, so <code class="d-inline-flex px-2 bg-success bg-opacity-10 border border-success border-opacity-10 rounded-2">48 65 6c 6c 6f</code> becomes <code class="d-inline-flex px-2 bg-success bg-opacity-10 border border-success border-opacity-10 rounded-2">6f 6c 6c 65 48</code>
            </p>
            <p class="px-2">
                The dropdown allows you to select a delimiter, which is how your hex values are split up and joined together. The default is a space, you can select no delimiter if your hex contains no spaces. 
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="collapse" id="{{ filename }}Collapse">
            <div class="col">
                <div class="card">
                    <span class="card-label visually-hidden">Reverse hex</span>
                    <div class="card-body text-center">
                        <textarea placeholder="Example: 47 56 37 47" title="Reverse hex nibbles" rows="6" id="{{ filename }}Text" class="form-control reverse-hex" autocomplete="off"></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-footer py-3">
                        <div class="text-center mb-4 g-0">
                            <div class="row row-cols-2 g-md-0 gx-0 gy-2">
                                <div class="col col-12 col-md-auto">
                                    <div class="input-group w-auto">
                                        <label class="input-group-text" for="{{ filename }}Delimiter"><span class="visually-hidden">Hex </span>Delimiter</label>
                                        {% include "components/delimiter" %}
                                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-md btn-convrtr me-2" id="{{ filename }}Decode">Reverse</button>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-12 col-md-auto flex-fill">
                                    <div class="row row-cols-auto g-0">
                                        <div class="col col-8 col-sm-auto ms-0 mx-md-2 me-auto">
                                            <div class="form-check form-switch text-start">
                                                <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" role="switch" id="reverseNibbles" aria-checked="false">
                                                <label class="form-check-label" for="reverseNibbles">Reverse Nibbles</label>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="col d-flex flex-fill justify-content-end">
                                            {% include "components/select-copy-dl" %}
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <hr />
                        <div id="{{ filename }}Results" class="data-to-copy active"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>